init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The movie is a comedy, but it is also a tragedy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is about the absurdity of life, and the fact that we are all alone in this world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The film was shot in the summer of 2015 in the Czech Republic.

actions.text: She was named Anna, and she was the youngest of five children.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She had a happy childhood, but her parents died in a car accident when she was only 14 years old.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was sent to an orphanage, where she met a boy named David.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They fell in love and ran away together.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They lived in a small cottage in the woods.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: David was a good man, but he had a dark secret.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was afraid of the dark, and he had to keep the lights on all night long.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: David was afraid that he would see a monster in the dark.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Anna was a good wife, and she tried to help him.
